Getting Inappropriate w/ You in Quiplash! ► http://bit.ly/GTLQuip

Game Lab has launched and we threw a party for all of our friends and fans! Unfortunately, we couldn't fly all of you out to LA, but we still wanted you to be a part of the celebration. We've invited Vsauce3, Jovenshire, Ronnie, and Drake onto the couch to learn more about their "darker" sides with a game of Will You Press the Button!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive
